{"tid":2156363,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[龍珠] 有無人鍾意比達多過格古洛","createTime":"2020-08-14T11:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T14:07:03.000Z","uid":272077,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0a0ffd3a0b458b4e93816d0bbf8f34ce4a572344","tid":2156363,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"格古洛, 點解你要存在係呢個世界上面?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我真係好討厭你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每一次對付強敵個陣, 你梗係要先我一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 而且我仲失敗到要你救返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 跟住到最後你仲可惡到死埋添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過今次... 今次唔同喇, 我一定會收拾個一隻怪物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你依家好好地訓返一覺先, 到你訓醒個陣, 一切都已經完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能連我亦都唔會再係呢一度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嘿...吓吓吓吓吓吓吓吓吓吓吓吓吓吓吓吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gi